<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>VIEFE - Herramienta de Orden de Compra</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Julius+Sans+One&family=Poppins:wght@500;600;700&family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/4.4.1/chart.umd.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/xlsx/0.18.5/xlsx.full.min.js"></script>
<style>
:root{
  /* Caribbean Cabinet Products brand palette (Booom 2021 brandbook) */
  --cc-black:#1a1a1a; --cc-orange:#c1602e; --cc-teal:#1b4d47; --cc-silver:#9aa0a6;
  --bg:#f4f3f1; --panel:#ffffff; --ink:#1a1a1a; --sub:#6a6f73; --line:#e4e1dc;
  --accent:#1b4d47; --accent-ink:#ffffff; --green:#1b4d47; --rowalt:#faf9f7; --radius:8px;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;}
body{margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink);font-family:'Open Sans',Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:13px;}
h1,h2,.family-name,.brand-word{font-family:'Poppins',Arial,sans-serif;}
header{background:var(--cc-black);color:#fff;padding:16px 22px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;}
header .brandmark{flex:0 0 auto;}
header .htext{flex:1;}
header h1{margin:0;font-size:18px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.03em;text-transform:uppercase;}
header h1 .brand-word{color:var(--cc-orange);}
header p{margin:3px 0 0;font-size:11px;color:#c9c9c9;}
.navback{background:transparent;color:#fff;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.35);border-radius:6px;padding:7px 12px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap;}
.navback:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);}
.wrap{padding:16px 22px 60px;}
.tabnav{display:flex;gap:4px;margin-bottom:16px;border-bottom:2px solid var(--line);position:sticky;top:0;background:var(--bg);z-index:10;padding-top:6px;}
.tabbtn{background:none;border:none;padding:10px 18px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--sub);cursor:pointer;border-bottom:3px solid transparent;margin-bottom:-2px;font-family:'Open Sans',Arial,sans-serif;}
.tabbtn:hover{color:var(--cc-teal);}
.tabbtn.active{color:var(--cc-teal);border-bottom-color:var(--accent);}
[data-tab]{display:none;}
[data-tab].tab-active{display:block;}
.panel{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:14px 16px;margin-bottom:14px;}
.panel h2{margin:0 0 10px;font-size:12px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;color:var(--cc-teal);font-weight:700;}
.row{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:14px;align-items:flex-end;}
.field{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px;}
.field label{font-size:11px;color:var(--sub);font-weight:600;}
input[type=text],input[type=number],select{
  border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:6px;padding:6px 8px;font-size:13px;background:#fff;color:var(--ink);
}
.tariff-toggle{display:flex;border:1px solid var(--accent);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;}
.tariff-toggle button{border:none;background:#fff;color:var(--accent);padding:7px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;}
.tariff-toggle button.active{background:var(--accent);color:#fff;}
.months-ctl{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;}
.months-ctl button{width:26px;height:26px;border:1px solid var(--line);background:#fff;border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent);}
.months-ctl input{width:60px;text-align:center;}
.chk{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:12px;color:var(--sub);}
button.btn{background:var(--accent);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:6px;padding:7px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;}
button.btn.secondary{background:#fff;color:var(--accent);border:1px solid var(--accent);}
#generatePoBtn{background:var(--cc-orange);}
button.btn.small{padding:4px 8px;font-size:11px;}
table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:12px;}
thead th{background:#eef1f5;border-bottom:2px solid var(--line);padding:6px;text-align:left;cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap;user-select:none;}
thead th.num{text-align:right;}
thead th:hover{background:#e2e7ee;}
tbody td{padding:5px 6px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);white-space:nowrap;}
tbody td.num{text-align:right;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;}
tbody tr:nth-child(even){background:var(--rowalt);}
tbody tr.row-in-epicor{background:#e5f5ea;}
tbody tr.row-in-epicor.has-order{background:#c9ecd6;}
tbody tr.row-not-epicor{background:#fbe1ea;}
tbody tr.gap-header-row td{font-weight:700;color:#9c2f57;padding:6px;}
tbody tr.no-price td{color:#aaa;}
.badge{display:inline-block;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;border-radius:4px;padding:1px 5px;margin-left:4px;}
.badge.warn{background:#fde2c8;color:#9a5b00;}
.badge.nop{background:#f0d3d3;color:#8a2020;}
.qty-input{width:60px;padding:3px 5px;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:5px;text-align:right;}
.summary-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:10px;}
.summary-item{background:#f7f8fa;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:6px;padding:8px 10px;}
.summary-item .lbl{font-size:10px;color:var(--sub);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.03em;}
.summary-item .val{font-size:17px;font-weight:700;margin-top:2px;}
.summary-item.total{background:var(--accent);color:#fff;}
.summary-item.total .lbl{color:#f3d9c8;}
.note{font-size:11px;color:var(--sub);line-height:1.5;margin-top:8px;}
.overlay{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(20,26,38,.55);z-index:50;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}
.overlay .box{background:#fff;border-radius:10px;max-width:560px;width:92%;max-height:80vh;overflow:auto;padding:20px 22px;}
.overlay .box h3{margin-top:0;}
.overlay .box textarea{width:100%;height:220px;font-family:monospace;font-size:11px;}
.closebtn{float:right;background:none;border:none;font-size:18px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--sub);}

.swatch{width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:4px;object-fit:cover;border:1px solid var(--line);vertical-align:middle;background:#eee;}
.swatch-sm{width:16px;height:16px;border-radius:3px;object-fit:cover;border:1px solid var(--line);vertical-align:middle;margin-right:4px;background:#eee;}
.hero-thumb{width:44px;height:44px;object-fit:contain;border-radius:6px;background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);flex:0 0 auto;cursor:pointer;transition:transform .1s;}
.hero-thumb:hover{transform:scale(1.15);border-color:var(--accent);}
.family-link{font-size:10px;color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px;}
.family-link:hover{text-decoration:underline;}
.chart-wrap{position:relative;max-height:640px;overflow-y:auto;overflow-x:hidden;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:6px;}
#chartInner{position:relative;min-height:420px;}
.chart-controls{display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:center;margin-bottom:10px;}

.mosaic-chip{border:none;background:none;padding:0;margin:0;cursor:pointer;line-height:0;}
.complete-bar-wrap{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;flex:0 0 auto;}
.complete-bar-bg{width:70px;height:7px;background:#e4e1dc;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;}
.complete-bar-fill{height:100%;border-radius:4px;}
.complete-pct{font-size:10.5px;font-weight:700;white-space:nowrap;}
.mosaic-chip:hover .swatch{outline:2px solid var(--accent);outline-offset:1px;}
.chip-btn{border:1px solid transparent;background:none;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:5px;cursor:pointer;font-size:12px;color:inherit;font-family:inherit;}
.chip-btn:hover{background:#e9ecef;border-color:var(--line);}
.size-chip{font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;}
.badge.disc{background:#e4d9d9;color:#6b3b3b;}
.badge.active{background:#e0ece6;color:#1b4d47;}
.local-filter-bar{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:6px 4px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.pill.active-pill{background:#e7efed;color:var(--accent);border:1px solid var(--accent);display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;}
.pill.active-pill .chip-btn{padding:0 4px;font-weight:700;}
.size-group-row td{background:#f0f2f0;font-weight:700;color:var(--cc-teal);padding:4px 6px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);}
.size-bracket{font-family:monospace;letter-spacing:.02em;}
.missing-block{padding:8px 10px;background:#fdf6ef;border-top:1px dashed var(--line);font-size:11px;}
.missing-block .pill{margin:3px 3px 0 0;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;}
.cov-crit{color:var(--red);font-weight:700;}
.cov-warn{color:#b8860b;font-weight:700;}
.cov-ok{color:var(--green);}

.statusbar{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:9px 22px;background:#eef3ea;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);font-size:12px;}
.statusbar.err{background:#fbeaea;}
.statusbar.loading{background:#eef1f5;}
.status-dot{width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--green);flex:0 0 auto;}
.status-dot.loading{background:#b8860b;}
.status-dot.err{background:var(--red);}
.statusbar .txt{flex:1;}
.upload-panel{display:none;}
.upload-panel.show{display:block;}
.filebtn{display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:var(--accent);border:1px solid var(--accent);border-radius:6px;padding:7px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;}
.filebtn input{display:none;}
.hidden{display:none !important;}

.family-card{border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius);margin-bottom:10px;background:#fff;overflow:hidden;}
.family-head{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:10px 12px;cursor:pointer;background:#f7f8fa;}
.family-head:hover{background:#eef1f5;}
.family-head .mosaic{display:flex;gap:2px;}
.family-name{font-weight:700;font-size:13px;flex:0 0 auto;min-width:150px;}
.family-meta{color:var(--sub);font-size:11px;flex:1;}
.family-total{font-weight:700;font-size:13px;color:var(--accent);white-space:nowrap;}
.family-caret{font-size:11px;color:var(--sub);width:14px;text-align:center;}
.family-body{display:none;padding:0 4px 8px;}
.family-body.open{display:block;}
.tablewrap{overflow:auto;max-height:420px;}
.pillrow{display:flex;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:6px;}
.pill{font-size:10px;background:#eef1f5;border-radius:10px;padding:2px 8px;color:var(--sub);}
.emptystate{padding:24px;text-align:center;color:var(--sub);font-size:13px;}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <button class="navback" id="navBackBtn">&#8592; Volver</button>
  <span class="brandmark">
    <svg width="34" height="34" viewBox="0 0 100 100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
      <g stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round">
        <line x1="50" y1="50" x2="50" y2="6"/>
        <line x1="50" y1="50" x2="68" y2="9" transform="rotate(11 50 50)"/>
        <line x1="50" y1="50" x2="50" y2="6" transform="rotate(22 50 50)"/>
        <line x1="50" y1="50" x2="50" y2="6" transform="rotate(33 50 50)"/>
        <line x1="50" y1="50" x2="50" y2="6" transform="rotate(44 50 50)"/>
        <line x1="50" y1="50" x2="50" y2="6" transform="rotate(55 50 50)"/>
        <line x1="50" y1="50" x2="50" y2="6" transform="rotate(66 50 50)"/>
        <line x1="50" y1="50" x2="50" y2="6" transform="rotate(77 50 50)"/>
        <line x1="50" y1="50" x2="50" y2="6" transform="rotate(88 50 50)"/>
      </g>
      <path d="M 50 50 A 35 35 0 1 0 78 22 L 50 50 Z" fill="#c1602e"/>
      <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="14" fill="#1a1a1a"/>
    </svg>
  </span>
  <div class="htext">
    <div style="font-family:'Julius Sans One',sans-serif;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:3.5px;color:#B4B2A9;margin-bottom:2px">CARIBBEAN <span style="font-size:7px;letter-spacing:2.5px;opacity:.75">CABINETS PRODUCTS</span></div>
    <h1>VIEFE &mdash; Orden de Compra</h1>
    <p>Vendor 18 &middot; Price List 2026 &middot; Agrupado por familia</p>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="statusbar loading" id="statusBar">
  <span class="status-dot loading" id="statusDot"></span>
  <span class="txt" id="statusTxt">Buscando reporte de inventario del hub...</span>
  <button class="btn secondary small" id="reloadHubBtn">Recargar desde hub</button>
  <button class="btn secondary small" id="showUploadBtn">Cargar archivo manualmente</button>
</div>

<div class="wrap upload-panel" id="uploadPanel">
  <div class="panel">
    <h2>Cargar reporte de inventario</h2>
    <p class="note">No se encontro el reporte en el hub (sessionStorage). Sube el archivo REPORTE_DE_MAS_DE_MENOS_TODOS_LOS_VEN.xlsx manualmente.</p>
    <label class="filebtn">Elegir archivo Excel<input type="file" id="fileInput"></label>
    <span class="note" id="fileStatus"></span>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="wrap hidden" id="mainWrap">

  <div class="tabnav">
    <button class="tabbtn active" data-tabbtn="orden">Orden</button>
    <button class="tabbtn" data-tabbtn="analisis">Analisis</button>
    <button class="tabbtn" data-tabbtn="catalogo">Catalogo VIEFE</button>
    <button class="tabbtn" data-tabbtn="po">Generar PO</button>
  </div>

  <div data-tab="orden">
  <div class="panel">
    <h2>Tarifa y cobertura</h2>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="field">
        <label>Tarifa</label>
        <div class="tariff-toggle">
          <button id="tariffUS" class="active">US / Canada (USD)</button>
          <button id="tariffES">Espana (EUR)</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>Meses de compra</label>
        <div class="months-ctl">
          <button id="monthsDown">-</button>
          <input type="number" id="monthsInput" value="12" step="0.1" min="0.1" max="36">
          <button id="monthsUp">+</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>Tasa de venta</label>
        <select id="rateMode">
          <option value="max" selected>MAX(L12M/12, Prom 3M)</option>
          <option value="l12">L12M / 12</option>
          <option value="p3m">Promedio ultimo 3 meses</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>&nbsp;</label>
        <button class="btn secondary small" id="resetQtyBtn">Recalcular sugeridos</button>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>&nbsp;</label>
        <button class="btn secondary small" id="rulesBtn">Ver reglas de descuento</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="panel">
    <h2>Filtros</h2>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="field">
        <label>Buscar SKU / descripcion</label>
        <input type="text" id="searchBox" placeholder="ej. CURVE, 0117...">
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>Familia</label>
        <select id="familyFilter"><option value="">Todas</option></select>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>Color / acabado</label>
        <select id="colorFilter"><option value="">Todos</option></select>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>Tamano (mm)</label>
        <select id="sizeFilter"><option value="">Todos</option></select>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>Descontinuados</label>
        <select id="discFilter">
          <option value="active" selected>Solo activos</option>
          <option value="all">Todos</option>
          <option value="disc">Solo descontinuados</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>&nbsp;</label>
        <button class="btn secondary small" id="clearFiltersBtn">Limpiar filtros</button>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>Ordenar familias por</label>
        <select id="familySort">
          <option value="volume" selected>Mas vendidas primero</option>
          <option value="alpha">Alfabetico</option>
          <option value="total">Total de la orden</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>&nbsp;</label>
        <div class="chk"><input type="checkbox" id="onlyOrder" checked><label for="onlyOrder">Solo con orden &gt; 0</label></div>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>&nbsp;</label>
        <button class="btn secondary small" id="expandAll">Expandir todo</button>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>&nbsp;</label>
        <button class="btn secondary small" id="collapseAll">Colapsar todo</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  </div>

  <div data-tab="analisis">
  <div class="panel">
    <h2>Analisis - Que tan movido esta</h2>
    <div class="chart-controls">
      <div class="field">
        <label>Agrupar por</label>
        <select id="chartDimension">
          <option value="family" selected>Familia</option>
          <option value="baseColor">Color (agrupado)</option>
          <option value="color">Color exacto</option>
          <option value="size">Tamano (mm)</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>Ordenar</label>
        <select id="chartSort">
          <option value="value" selected>Mayor a menor</option>
          <option value="alpha">Alfabetico (A-Z)</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>Metrica</label>
        <select id="chartMetric">
          <option value="l12" selected>Unidades vendidas (L12M)</option>
          <option value="revenue">Ingresos L12M estimados</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>Mostrar</label>
        <select id="chartTop">
          <option value="15">Top 15</option>
          <option value="25">Top 25</option>
          <option value="40">Top 40</option>
          <option value="50">Top 50</option>
          <option value="9999" selected>Todas</option>
          <option value="custom">Personalizado...</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="field" id="chartTopCustomWrap" style="display:none;">
        <label>Cuantas</label>
        <input type="number" id="chartTopCustom" value="30" min="1" max="500" style="width:70px;">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="chart-wrap"><div id="chartInner"><canvas id="familyChart"></canvas></div></div>
    <p class="note">Este analisis usa el historico completo de ventas (L12M), independiente de los filtros de arriba, para que puedas comparar que se mueve realmente.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="panel">
    <h2>Tendencia mensual de ventas</h2>
    <p class="note">Usa las columnas de ventas por mes de tu reporte (hasta 13 meses) para ver si el negocio esta subiendo o bajando.</p>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="field">
        <label>Ver</label>
        <select id="trendScope">
          <option value="total" selected>Total VIEFE</option>
          <option value="family">Por familia especifica</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="field" id="trendFamilyWrap" style="display:none;">
        <label>Familia</label>
        <select id="trendFamily"></select>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="chart-wrap" style="max-height:340px;"><div id="trendInner" style="height:300px;"><canvas id="trendChart"></canvas></div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="panel">
    <h2>Riesgo de quiebre de stock</h2>
    <p class="note">
      SKUs activos ordenados por cobertura actual (QOH / tasa de venta mensual), de menor a mayor.
      Rojo = menos de 1 mes de cobertura. Ambar = menos de 3 meses.
    </p>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="field">
        <label>Mostrar</label>
        <select id="riskLimit">
          <option value="20" selected>Top 20 mas criticos</option>
          <option value="50">Top 50 mas criticos</option>
          <option value="9999">Todos los que tengan menos de 3 meses</option>
        </select>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tablewrap" style="margin-top:10px;">
      <table>
        <thead><tr><th>SKU</th><th>Familia</th><th>Descripcion</th><th class="num">QOH</th><th class="num">Tasa/mes</th><th class="num">Cobertura</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody id="riskList"></tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>

  </div>

  <div data-tab="orden">
  <div class="panel">
    <h2>Familias</h2>
    <p class="note">Las fotos de producto se cargan automaticamente desde el catalogo VIEFE; si una foto no esta disponible, se muestra el mosaico de colores reales de esa familia en su lugar.</p>
    <div id="familyList"></div>
  </div>
  </div>

  <div data-tab="catalogo">
  <div class="panel">
    <h2>Familias Incompletas - Que Te Falta de VIEFE</h2>
    <p class="note">
      Por cada familia: cuantas variantes (color/tamano) tienes creadas en Epicor de las que existen
      en el catalogo VIEFE 2026, con la lista exacta de lo que falta. Ordenado de la familia mas
      incompleta a la mas completa, para que reconozcas rapido donde tienes huecos de catalogo.
    </p>
    <div class="row">
      <button class="btn secondary small" id="gapsExpandAll">Expandir todo</button>
      <button class="btn secondary small" id="gapsCollapseAll">Colapsar todo</button>
    </div>
    <div id="gapsList" style="margin-top:10px;"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="panel">
    <h2>En tu Epicor pero NO en la lista de precios VIEFE 2026</h2>
    <p class="note">
      SKUs de VIEFE que existen en tu reporte de inventario pero no coinciden con ningun codigo de la
      lista de precios 2026 (NA + EU). Usualmente son modelos descontinuados o con numeracion antigua.
    </p>
    <div id="invGapsList" style="margin-top:10px;"></div>
  </div>

  </div>

  <div data-tab="orden">
  <div class="panel">
    <h2>Resumen de la orden</h2>
    <div class="row" style="margin-bottom:10px;">
      <div class="chk"><input type="checkbox" id="budgetEnabled"><label for="budgetEnabled">Limitar orden por presupuesto</label></div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>Presupuesto maximo</label>
